        <p class="editorial-body"><span class="drop-cap">A</span>Iceberg Mind is a deep dive into the <strong>joy of discovery</strong> and the <strong>beauty of thinking</strong>, from the earliest spark to the lifelong wonder of the mind.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block" style="position: relative;">
        <p class="pullquote">It's a space where <strong>science meets imagination</strong>, where <strong>learning becomes play</strong>, and where artificial intelligence helps reveal what lies beneath the surface — not by teaching what to think, but by opening <strong>paths to think differently</strong>.</p>
